{"tid":1054530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之前有個人話兩公婆做譚仔買樓就好易","createTime":"2019-03-10T01:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T12:30:17.000Z","uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f442f485649a4acb70041d44dd513f2417e996e","tid":1054530,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"延伸落去，如果兩公婆做譚仔，之後老爺奶奶外父外母都一齊做譚仔，之後生4個，養大之後4個一齊去做譚仔，結咗婚之後又一齊做譚仔，生埋個孫個孫又做譚仔，咪成家可以買千萬樓做千萬富翁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後叫啲親戚一齊去做譚仔，咪成個家族都有幾間千萬樓，到時真係揚威海外囉，做譚仔做到發達，重勁過中六合彩頭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時譚仔入職可能重難過入上市公司做MT或者經理同埋政府工，隨時要過五關斬六將，考體能、考發音、考能力傾向、考多國語言、...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7c48e79d5a68974e1c05493d4fac3456c68290","tid":1054530,"uid":218443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想到就做 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff617a90e41a4769131e9af54148706eeb9081b","tid":1054530,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc7c48e79d5a68974e1c05493d4fac3456c68290","tid":1054530,"uid":218443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想到就做 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dd599a3ca7a2a958767a086641e32dde8e9678","tid":1054530,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"on9你都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":